ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Kwets'ootł'àà (North Arm of Great Slave Lake)) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (NORTH ARM OF GREAT SLAVE LAKE) ORDER which withdraws from disposal the surface and subsurface rights to certain lands, for a period of two years, in order to facilitate the establishment of a National Wildlife Area.
